  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Encrypted Navigation Data",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "破译的导航数据",
    "TencentChinese": "破译的导航数据",
    "TraditionalChinese": "加密導航資料"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Encoded navigation data which, when properly decrypted, will reveal the location of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Drop Pod</span> containing an Exosuit <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Inventory Upgrade</span>.<br><br>Select the coordinates in the inventory and use <span class=\"name name-technology\">Plot Route</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) to pin the location in your Exosuit display.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "加密导航数据，若成功破译，就能定位一个含有套装<span class=\"name name-stellar\">库存升级</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">空降舱</span>。<br><br>在库存中选择坐标并使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">规划路线</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）在你的套装显示屏上标记位置。",
    "TencentChinese": "输入<span class=\"name name-technology\">信号增强器</span>即可编码导航数据。<br><br>正确解码后能揭示一处含有<span class=\"name name-special\">套装升级</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">空降舱</span>的位置。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "加密導航資訊在正確解密後，會揭露內含強化套裝<span class=\"name name-stellar\">道具欄升級</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">空投艙</span>位置。<br><br>選擇道具欄中的座標，並使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">規劃路線</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)，即可在你的強化套裝顯示器中釘選該地點。"
  },
